qrcodegen
------------------------------------------
This project aims to be the best, clearest QR Code generator library in
multiple languages. The primary goals are flexible options and absolute
correctness. Secondary goals are compact implementation size and good
documentation comments.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libqrcodegen-devel-1.8.0-1bl1
  libqrcodegen1-1.8.0-1bl1
  libqrcodegencpp-devel-1.8.0-1bl1
  libqrcodegencpp1-1.8.0-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/nayuki/QR-Code-generator

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/nayuki/QR-Code-generator/archive/refs/tags/v1.8.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack qrcodegen-1.8.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./qrcodegen-1.8.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/qrcodegen-1.8.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/qrcodegen-1.8.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libqrcodegen1-1.8.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libqrcodegen-devel-1.8.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libqrcodegencpp1-1.8.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libqrcodegencpp-devel-1.8.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(qrcodegen)
  /usr/bin/qrcodegen-demo.exe
  /usr/bin/qrcodegen-test.exe
  /usr/bin/qrcodegencpp-demo.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/qrcodegen.README
  /usr/share/doc/qrcodegen/Readme.markdown

(libqrcodegen1)
  /usr/bin/cygqrcodegen-1.dll

(libqrcodegen-devel)
  /usr/include/qrcodegen/qrcodegen.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegen/qrcodegen-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegen/qrcodegen-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegen/qrcodegen-targets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegen/qrcodegen-targets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libqrcodegen.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/qrcodegen.pc

(libqrcodegencpp1)
  /usr/bin/cygqrcodegencpp-1.dll

(libqrcodegencpp-devel)
  /usr/include/qrcodegencpp/qrcodegen.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegencpp/qrcodegencpp-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegencpp/qrcodegencpp-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegencpp/qrcodegencpp-targets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/qrcodegencpp/qrcodegencpp-targets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libqrcodegencpp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/qrcodegencpp.pc

